Cat Ninja is a popular online flash game where players control a fast and agile ninja cat on a mission to complete various levels filled with traps, obstacles, and enemies. The game combines platforming, puzzle solving and action elements. Now you can play directly on Chrome browser thanks to the Chrome extension without having to download and without ads!

Gameplay typically involves controlling the cat ninja through each level, using jumping and wall-climbing abilities to avoid hazards such as spikes, enemy creatures, and other hazards. The cat ninja may also have some fighting moves or tools to defeat enemies or overcome obstacles.

Players often encounter increasingly challenging levels of increasing difficulty, requiring precise timing, quick reflexes and problem solving to progress. Some levels may have hidden secrets or collectibles to find, adding to the replayability of the game.

The game's appeal lies in its charming and cute visuals coupled with challenging gameplay, making it appealing to players of various skill levels.

Cat Ninja has become popular across various gaming platforms and websites due to its addictive nature and entertaining gameplay, attracting players looking for a fun and challenging experience.
